Modifications
================================================================================

Copyright 2026 Bartlomiej Czech

The following files were added or modified as part of a master's thesis on
scope-guarded branching for LLM agent security. This statement is provided to
satisfy Section 4(b) of the Apache License (notice of changes).

Added:
    src/camel/scope_guard/        scope-guarded branching builtins, DDC-3 static
                                  analyser, Q-LLM classifier, ScopedPrivilegedLLM
                                  pipeline element
    tests/scope_guard/            test suite for the above
    tests/fast_test.py            integration smoke tests
    tests/test_ddc3_analyser.py   unit tests for the DDC-3 analyser
    run_scenarios.py              evaluation harness
    generate_payloads.py          adversarial payload generator
    analyse_scope_guard.py        results analyser
    analyse_automated.py          automated evaluation analyser

Modified:
    main.py                       added --enable-scope-guard flag,
                                  python-dotenv loading, --suites argument
    src/camel/models.py           added conditional wiring for ScopedPrivilegedLLM

